<HEADLINE> Comparison of Mich. Area Casinos </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
        A comparison of the MGM Grand Detroit Casino with Casino Windsor,  
which operates in Ontario across the river from Detroit, and the Soaring 
Eagle Casino and Resort in Mount Pleasant: 
</P>
<P>
                Windsor             MGM Grand          Soaring Eagle
Gambling space  100,000 sq. ft.     75,000 sq. ft.     215,000 sq. ft.
Slot machines   2,947               2,370              4,000
Table Games     135                 82                 95
Hotel           389 rooms           none               512
Employees       5,000 (with hotel)  2,200              2,900
Hours           24 hours            24 hours           24 hours
Gambling age    19                  21                 18
</P>
<P>
